        "Abstract": "This paper presents the Belgian Statutory Article Retrieval Dataset (BSARD), a novel dataset for statutory article retrieval in French. The dataset consists of 1,100+ legal questions posed by Belgian citizens and labeled by legal experts with references to relevant articles from a corpus of 22,600+ Belgian law articles. We benchmark several state-of-the-art retrieval approaches on BSARD and show that fine-tuned dense retrieval models significantly outperform other systems."
